<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vailam thing cung ka zoh tikah, Sunparnak Bawi kha ka hmuh i, Porhlawt
 le ruamkainak vialte, Atu zei ah ka rel ti lo.

[V2]
 Pathian Bawi Khrih thihnak hlei in, Ruamkainak dang zeihmanh um lo;
 Zeizong ka lungchung duhnak kha, A thihnak ca pek ka duh ko.

[V3]
 A kut, ke le a lu zoh tuah, Ngaihchiat le zaangfah an luang ti, Cu
 bang in an i tong kho maw, A lu hling in chinh a tlak maw?

[V4]
 Ka ngeih vialte pe hmanh ninglaw, Laksawng a tam tuk bal lai lo, A
 sung bik zaangfahnak caah, Pum le thlarau pek ka duh ko.</lyrics>
<title>VAILAMTAH KA HUN ZOH TIKAH CH125</title>
<hymn_number>125</hymn_number>
</song>